<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
The game of ToME is a single player dungeon simulation.  A player may choose from a number of races and classes when creating a character, and then "run" that character over a period of days, weeks, even months, attempting to win the game by completing his quests. <p>
The player will begin his adventure on the town level where he may acquire supplies, weapons, armour, and magical devices by bartering with various shop owners. After preparing for his adventure, the player can descend into the dungeon near Bree where fantastic adventures await his coming! 
</p>
<p>
You will probably need to browse through the <a href="./Documentation">Documentation</a> files, especially the one on available <a class="nonexistent" href="./Commands">Commands</a>, before beginning any serious adventuring. Reading the <a class="nonexistent" href="./ToME_20FAQ">ToME FAQ</a> is also highly recommended. 
</p>
</div><div id="footer">


